Yeah, in the future when we need it, we'll go ahead and send you a stamped envelope or something,

20:39.140 --> 20:42.300
and if you wouldn't bother, it wouldn't be a bother, you can send us one.

20:42.420 --> 20:42.780
I appreciate that.

20:43.140 --> 20:45.200
I'll get a photograph off to you today or tomorrow.

20:45.880 --> 20:48.000
Okay, then thank you, Mr. Rogen. We sure appreciate your time.

20:48.440 --> 20:49.500
Okay, I appreciate your interest.

